1
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:58,410
Something's wrong.

2
00:00:58,840 --> 00:01:00,320
The parts have been replaced.

3
00:01:00,320 --> 00:01:00,920
What?

4
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:03,720
There is wear on the surface,

5
00:01:03,720 --> 00:01:05,580
and signs of intentional damage.

6
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:07,000
It was done very cleanly.

7
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:21,600
No wonder you insisted on inspecting the car again.

8
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:24,200
It's truly hard to guard against an inside job.

9
00:01:28,039 --> 00:01:28,520
Hello?

10
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:29,840
Hello.

11
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:31,960
Is this Mr. Bai Tianyu?

12
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:34,520
I'm a representative from Haojie Finance.

13
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:35,720
Your brother, Liu Yaqi,

14
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:37,680
borrowed 30,000 yuan on our platform.

15
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:39,080
It is three days overdue.

16
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:40,700
When will you settle this?

17
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:43,479
Okay, I got it.

18
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:49,450
Where are you going?

19
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:01,800
Stop right there.

20
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:06,320
It seems you know you did something wrong, right?

21
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:07,920
Let go. I didn't do anything.

22
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:08,960
Where are the parts?

23
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:09,600
Put them all back.

24
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:11,200
What's going on here?

25
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:14,080
I don't know what you're talking about. I have things to do.

26
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,320
If you leave today,

27
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:16,880
don't ever come back.

28
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,360
Don't think that just because you stole the parts from Mr. Dong's car,

29
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,290
no one will know.

30
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:21,680
No way.

31
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:23,340
They actually swap parts.

32
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:24,760
Could it be a shady shop?

33
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:25,920
This is too much.

34
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:29,960
Little girl, don't talk nonsense in public.

35
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:30,680
How am I talking nonsense?

36
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,280
Um.

37
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,160
I...

38
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,800
Did I hear that right?

39
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:38,540
Was she just talking about my car?

40
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,240
Why didn't you answer my calls?

41
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:45,240
I happened to be passing by and wanted to pick up my car.

42
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,040
Your car...

43
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:49,840
You probably can't pick it up today.

44
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,600
Why?

45
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:53,360
Then...

46
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,850
So what she said is true.

47
00:02:56,720 --> 00:02:58,920
My car just needed an oil change.

48
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:00,880
I am the owner.

49
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:03,080
You changed the parts without my permission.

50
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,480
Do you know what kind of car that is?

51
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,960
Can you afford to pay for it?

52
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,620
What kind of behavior is this?

53
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,360
It's a violation, illegal,

54
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,640
and theft!

55
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:12,580
Let me tell you.

56
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:15,000
As long as I, Dong Dawei, am in Lucheng,

57
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:17,079
your shop won't survive here.

58
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:17,520
Got it?

59
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,240
He is also a victim.

60
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,700
Why are you only mad at him?

61
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,130
Alright, stop talking.

62
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,760
Fine, let's not argue.

63
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:24,720
Let's go.

64
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,320
Take me to see the car.

65
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:37,200
I will never go to his place to fix my car again.

66
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:37,840
Yes.

67
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,400
Tianyu, listen to me, let me explain.

68
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,520
I really didn't mean to do it.

69
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,440
I just did it because I...

70
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,720
Why did you bring up Yaqi changing parts

71
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:45,120
in front of so many people?

72
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:47,240
If I hadn't refunded them and fixed the car again,

73
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:49,079
do you know how serious the consequences would be?

74
00:03:49,079 --> 00:03:51,200
But I really just wanted to defend you,

75
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:51,760
so I did that.

76
00:03:51,760 --> 00:03:52,620
I don't need it.

77
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:01,280
Then,

78
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:05,620
just consider me being a busybody, okay?

79
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,200
Forget it.

80
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:23,880
Brother Meng.

81
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,360
Um,

82
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,820
can you lend me some money?

83
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:31,600
I'm a bit tight on cash lately.

84
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,400
You'll have to find another way.

85
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,320
It's fine.

86
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:37,240
Let's keep in touch.

87
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:38,560
Okay.

88
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:53,200
Tianyu has gone too far.

89
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:55,960
You can't be blamed for this.

90
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,360
You were just trying to protect him.

91
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,520
He's so inexplicable.

92
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:06,960
I can't explain it to you anyway.

93
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:13,600
Hello.

94
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:16,520
I'm Gao Chenyang from Lu University's Design Department.

95
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:17,200
I was just watching.

96
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:19,520
You're painting the outer wall of the animal shelter.

97
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:20,440
Can I join you?

98
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:22,160
Sure.

99
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,440
Why are you staring at me?

100
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:45,180
Is there something on my face?

101
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:45,840
No.

102
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:48,760
Junior sister, I was drawing a rabbit just now.

103
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,560
I think you're as cute as a rabbit.

104
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:52,090
I drew it based on your face.

105
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,040
Look at me.

106
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:56,680
What small animal do I look like?

107
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:57,360
Sorry.

108
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:59,520
I have no interest in observing you.

109
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:02,200
Who cares to observe you?

110
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:03,840
Thank you.

111
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,580
Junior sister,

112
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:07,000
if it's convenient for you,

113
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:09,060
could you leave me your contact info?

114
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:11,280
No need, senior.

115
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:12,440
What I mean is,

116
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:14,640
next time if I see stray animals,

117
00:06:14,840 --> 00:06:16,640
I want to contact you right away.

118
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,930
Let's keep in touch.

119
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:32,840
Goodbye, senior.

120
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,840
Goodbye, junior sister.

121
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,720
He likes you.

122
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,080
Don't be ridiculous.

123
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:46,460
Otherwise, why didn't he observe me?

124
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,050
That's too much.

125
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,420
I have to talk to him when he gets back.

126
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:53,600
Yaqi.

127
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:57,540
Did you take out an online loan this time,

128
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:58,840
chase girls,

129
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,360
or go gambling?

130
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:01,520
Tell us yourself.

131
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:02,560
No.

132
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:05,600
I just invested in some stocks with friends

133
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:07,440
and accidentally lost money.

134
00:07:07,440 --> 00:07:08,480
I didn't know how to tell you,

135
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,320
so I...

136
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:10,720
All day long,

137
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,120
it's either stocks

138
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,610
or lottery tickets.

139
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:15,680
Can't you learn from your brother

140
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,960
and work dependably?

141
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:19,680
Are you planning to be a good-for-nothing your whole life?

142
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,320
It's enough to have him in the shop.

143
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,800
I wanted to try other options.

144
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,660
That's why I...

145
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,640
What options?

146
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:26,410
What kind of option is this?

147
00:07:26,840 --> 00:07:28,640
You don't learn the good things,

148
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:31,760
and instead learned to steal and sell parts?

149
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,840
If your brother hadn't told me,

150
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:36,040
did you ever consider the serious consequences?

151
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,800
Yes, I was wrong.

152
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:41,040
But is that woman totally faultless?

153
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,240
If it weren't for her,

154
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:43,960
would we have lost so much money

155
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:45,220
and so many customers?

156
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:46,920
If our store goes bankrupt one day,

157
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,920
it will be all because of that woman.

158
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:53,280
You're fighting me over a woman.

159
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,159
You're so gutless now

160
00:07:56,159 --> 00:07:58,520
that you need a woman to take the blame, right?

161
00:07:58,520 --> 00:08:00,040
If you don't learn a lesson now,

162
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,700
your life is ruined, you know?

163
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:04,090
You've taken all my benefits my whole life

164
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:06,120
and kept me under your thumb.

165
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,610
So what if I cause a little trouble?

166
00:08:08,640 --> 00:08:10,720
Aren't you able to handle everything?

167
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,600
I just want to make you miserable.

168
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:15,560
I...

169
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:19,080
Really.

170
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,400
This kid.

171
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:21,920
Tianyu,

172
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:23,700
don't take it to heart.

173
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,640
If you like that girl,

174
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:26,560
go for it.

175
00:08:27,080 --> 00:08:28,280
Don't let yourself regret it.

176
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:30,740
We are not in that kind of relationship, Dad.

177
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,799
Let me push you back to bed first.

178
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,929
I still have a car to repair.

179
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:40,159
Hurry up.

180
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:42,720
If you don't compensate us today, no one will have a good time.

181
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,240
No,

182
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:45,960
we already handled this compensation yesterday.

183
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,560
Besides,

184
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,080
we really can't give a refund.

185
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,080
I'm really sorry.

186
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,800
You can't give a refund? Is that it?

187
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,440
Go get the car out for me right now.

188
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:56,370
The whole street knows about this.

189
00:08:56,520 --> 00:08:57,400
Who would dare to get their car repaired here?

190
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:58,160
Exactly. Yeah.

191
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,240
No, listen to me.

192
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,520
Give me my car right now.

193
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:01,960
Did you dismantle our parts

194
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:02,400
and sell them?

195
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:04,800
Yeah! Compensate us!

196
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:05,760
Give me my car.

197
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,320
You ruined my car.

198
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:08,400
No.

199
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,280
Refund our money.

200
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:09,800
No.

201
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,920
Just listen to my explanation!

202
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:12,120
Listen to me explain.

203
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:14,600
I've repaired everything that needed fixing.

204
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:16,400
Do you expect me to take it all apart again for you?

205
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:18,200
We have no idea what parts you used.

206
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,520
What if they're illegal?

207
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:20,560
What nonsense are you talking about?

208
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:22,560
We just want to take our cars back.

209
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:23,360
What kind of place...

210
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:23,640
What are you doing?

211
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:24,360
...is this? What's going on here?

212
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:25,560
We just want our cars.

213
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,720
You can take your cars,

214
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,600
but we can't refund your money.

215
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,160
You can take them to any repair shop

216
00:09:31,160 --> 00:09:31,920
for inspection.

217
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:33,920
If you can prove there's a problem with our work,

218
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:34,680
we'll compensate you tenfold.
